# tonespeak eval secrets -- project-scoped, NOT system-wide.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your key after the `=`.
# `.env.local` is gitignored:  it is never committed and never leaves your machine.
# The eval harness (evals/three-arm-eval.js) loads `.env.local` then `.env`
# automatically;  a real environment variable, if already set, takes precedence.
#
# Required only for `--strict` (bare-mode) runs -- see evals/README.md.
# Generate a key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
